PRICING FAQS
------------

*   [#### How long does it take to get started?](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    **Getting started with Wicked Reports**  
      
    CRM, Cart, and Ad platform integrations each take about 1 minute.
    
    Tracking script can be deployed via Google Tag Manager in 2 minutes.
    
    Manual tracking script deployment depends on your tech stack.
    
    API integrations depend on your dev team, [see our API documentation here.](https://docs.wickedreports.com/)
    
*   [#### What happens after 14 days?](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    You are billed for your regular monthly subscription cost based on your CRM contacts.
    
    See the visual guide to Wicked Reports success for a blueprint of how Wicked helps digital marketers thrive using attribution data.
    
*   [#### Will I be stuck in a contract?](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Plans are monthly, cancel anytime.
    
    Annual pre-pay contracts are an option that many of our happy customers choose, which saves you up to 2 months on cost.
    
*   [#### Can I change plans?](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Yes, you can change your Wicked Reports subscription. It's easy - just chat live at any time with an agent to change your plan.
    
*   [#### I still have questions, who do I ask?](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    [**Book a live zoom**](https://www.wickedreports.com/get-wicked-now) or **[email us](mailto:sales@wickedreports.com)** \- we are happy to talk about solutions for your marketing attribution needs.

Marketing attribution problems & solutions
------------------------------------------

*   [#### It's hard to set up my marketing attribution correctly](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Wicked Reports has _**easy, 1-minute integrations**_ with Klaviyo, Shopify, and ReCharge.
    
*   [#### The numbers just don't make sense inside my existing dashboard](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    On-demand Wicked Insights analyze your data _**with you**_!
    
    Plus, our Dedicated Customer Success managers  provide live zoom trainings.
    
*   [#### I can't tie revenue back to marketing](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Wicked Reports shows order level details for all sales conversion data.
    
*   [#### It's too hard to understand and act on my attribution data](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Wicked Playbooks provide step by step instructions and video.
    
    Wicked Insights analyze your data with you on-demand.
    
    Dedicated Customer Success manager that provides live zoom training
    
    Live Chat 24/5
    
*   [#### I don't understand my Customer LTV](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Cohort reports provide the framework to understand Customer LTV
    
    Wicked Playbook and Insights give you the keys to analyze, understand, and act on the data.
    
*   [#### I've tried to use other tools for marketing attribution and I can't get them to work](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Your dedicated Wicked CSM is responsible for helping you succeed.
    
*   [#### Facebook's attribution window is too short](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Facebook's 7-day attribution look back window is not enough time for you to learn and understand your customer's journey. Wicked Reports shows lifetime revenue attribution, from the very first click to the very last click, and all the touch points in between.
    
*   [#### I've tried other platforms and they aren't accurate](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Wicked Reports transparently shows attribution percentage and ALL clicks, leads, and sales tracked.
    
    This is the importance of using first-party attribution data, rather than relying on what a platform (like Facebook) is saying. Those numbers are often inflated and take credit for sales they didn't see, plus, the look back window is TOO SHORT. Also, they can't give you an accurate overall picture of your marketing.
    
*   [#### Sometimes I need help but please don't make me watch a ton of videos or get on another Zoom](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    You're in luck!  
      
    Our Live Chat feature is a super quick way to request help - and a live person will answer you!  
      
    If you are going to handle the onboarding yourself and do not require assistance from our support team, we can waive the onboarding fee for you and allow you to start paying your monthly subscription charges immediately.  
      
    Please talk to your sales rep for additional details.
    
*   [#### I don't want to spend any more money on another marketing attribution tool](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Ecommerce marketers realize that in order to get a clear picture of **what every marketing dollar is doing, an external tool that provides first party data is not an added expense. It is a necessary secret weapon in scaling ROAS and seeing huge ROI.**
    
    Wicked Reports actually identifies wasted ad spend GREATER than the cost of Wicked.
    
*   [#### I can't see all my paid performance in one place](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    Wicked Reports has deep cost integrations with Facebook, Google, Microsoft / Bing, Pinterest, SnapChat, TikTok and more.   
      
    This means you can see how all your marketing is working, all in one place. Compare campaigns and ad performance with our ROI grid and compare channels with each other for best performance.
    
*   [#### It's hard to setup a marketing attribution software](https://www.wickedreports.com/pricing#)
    
    It's easy to setup all your platform integrations inside Wicked Reports. Simply provide authorizations one time, and in under 60 seconds, your accounts are synced with Wicked Reports.
